.\" Manpage for hex
.TH man 1 "31 October 2024" "1.0" "hex man page"
.SH NAME
hex \- Convert binary data to raw hex data
.SH SYNOPSIS
hex [input] [output]
.SH OPTIONS
input is either a file or "STDIN"

output is either a file, "STDOUT", "STDERR" or blank for a .hex file
Warning: If output is ommitted, input must not be "STDIN"
.SH EXAMPLES
hex data.bin
Will read from data.bin and write to data.bin.hex

hex STDIN STDOUT
Will read from stdin and print to stdout, reccommended for use with pipes
.SH SEE ALSO
unhex(1)
.SH BUGS
None \- My code is perfect
